mentMethodInstantDisclaimerParagraph:"If you choose this payment method, you will be charged instantly.",PaymentMethodInstantDisclaimerParagraph1:"If you choose this payment method, you will be charged instantly. No funds will be paid out to the creator until the campaign ends successfully. If the campaign doesn't end successfully, you'll get a full refund.",PaymentMethodInstantDisclaimerParagraph2:"You'll be able to upgrade your pledge freely.",PaymentMethodInstantDisclaimerParagraph3:"Once paid, all pledge upgrades must be settled using the same payment method.",PaymentMethodInstantDisclaimerParagraph4:"If you change your mind, you can ask the creator to cancel your pledge and receive a full refund up until the end of the crowdfunding campaign.",PaymentMethodInstantDisclaimerParagraph5:"After the campaign ends successfully, standard campaign cancelation policy applies.",PaymentMethodInstantDisclaimerParagraph6:"After the campaign ends, standard campaign cancelation policy applies.",PaymentMethodInstantDisclaimerParagraph7:"If you change your mind, you can ask the creator to cancel your pledge and request a refund up until the end of the crowdfunding campaign.",PaymentNotFoundErrorMessage:"Payment was not found.",PaymentProcessingBoxActionLabel:"Go to project page",PaymentProcessingDeferredBoxDescription:" We're currently verifying your payment details. This may take up to {0} {1}, depending on your payment provider. The payment will only be collected if the campaign ends successfully. Until then, you can freely change or withdraw your pledge. You may stay here to see the result or continue browsing. We'll email you once the verification is complete.",PaymentProcessingDeferredBoxTitle:"Verifying payment method",PaymentProcessingInstantBoxDescription:"We're processing your payment now. For selected payment method, it may take up to {0} {1}. You may wait here for result or continue browsing. We will email you with the operation result.",PaymentProcessingInstantBoxTit